{"lemma":"أَداةٌ","slug":"أَداةٌ","root":"#.د.#","root_slug":"_-د-_","root_link":"/words/roots/_-د-_","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":6},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n462","n468"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%A3%D9%8E%D8%AF%D8%A7%D8%A9%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"device, tool, instrument"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"utensil, implement"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"appliance"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"apparatus"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"machinery"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"particle"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":["/ʔa.daːh/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n462","headword_ar":"اَدَاةٌ","root":"Adw","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An instrument; a tool; an implement; a utensil:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"instruments; tools; implements; utensils; apparatus; equipments; equipage; accoutrements; furniture; gear; tackling:"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A=lapN","text_ar":"ا=لَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (T, S, M, Msb, K:) of any tradesman or craftsman; with which he performs the work of his trade or craft: and of war;"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^adaApu AlHarobi","text_ar":"اَدَاةُ الحَرْبِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifying"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"weapons,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"arms:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, T:) and for an affair [of any kind]: (M:) [applied also to the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"apparatus"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a camel, or of a camel's saddle, &c.: (see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HidojN","text_ar":"حِدْجٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":":)] and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_idaAwapN","text_ar":"اـِدَاوَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies the same; (M, TA;) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^adaAwapN","text_ar":"اَدَاوَةٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (TA:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^adiY~N","text_ar":"اَدِىٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, TA,) like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"ganiY~N","text_ar":"غَنِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (TA,) [in some copies of the S"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A=diY~N","text_ar":"ا=دِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":",] signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"apparatus,"},{"kind":"page_break","n":38},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"equipments, equipage, accoutrements, furniture, gear, tackling, implements, tools,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^uhobapN","text_ar":"اُهْبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, TA:) the pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^adaAhN","text_ar":"اَدَاهٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^adawaAtN","text_ar":"اَدَوَاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (T, S, Msb, K.) You say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^axa*a A^adaAtahu","text_ar":"اَخَذَ اَدَاتَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He took his apparatus,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.; or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"prepared, furnished, equipped,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"accoutred, himself"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; (S, M, K;)"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"liloA^amori","text_ar":"لِلْاَمْرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for the affair"},{"kind":"text","text":"], and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lils~afari","text_ar":"لِلسَّفَرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for journeying,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the journey"},{"kind":"text","text":"], (M,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lild~ahori","text_ar":"لِلدَّهْرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"for"},{"kind":"text","text":"the vicissitudes of"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fortune"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (T, S, K:) and it is related on the authority of Ks, that they said"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^axa*a hadaAtahu","text_ar":"اَخَذَ هَدَاتَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; substituting"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"h","text_ar":"ه"},{"kind":"text","text":"for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^","text_ar":"ا"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Lh, M). And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^xa*otu li*`lika","text_ar":"اخَذْتُ لِذٰلِكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA^amor A^adiy~ahu","text_ar":"الاَمْر اَدِيَّهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^uhobatahu","text_ar":"اُهْبَتَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I took for that affair its apparatus,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.]. (S, TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naHonu EalaY","text_ar":"نَحْنُ عَلَى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lilS~alaApi","text_ar":"لِلصَّلَاةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^adiY~K","text_ar":"اَدِىٍّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"We are in a state of preparation for prayer."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA.) ―         -b2-  [Hence, in grammar,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A particle;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as being a kind of auxiliary; including the article"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Al","text_ar":"ال"},{"kind":"text","text":", the preposition, the conjunction, and the interjection; but not the adverbial noun.]"}],"source_refs":["T","S","M","Msb","K","Lth","TA","Lh"]},{"entry_id":"n468","headword_ar":"ادّاهُ","root":"AdY","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (T, S, M, &c.,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tA^NdiyapN","text_ar":"تاٌدِيَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, S, K) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^adaA='N","text_ar":"اَدَا=ءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (T,) or the latter is a simple subst., (S, M, Msb, K,) [and so, accord. to the Msb, is the former also, but this is a mistake,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He made it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"caused it, to reach, arrive,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"come"},{"kind":"text","text":"[to the appointed person or place &c.];"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he brought, conveyed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"delivered, it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"syn."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^awoSalahu","text_ar":"اَوْصَلَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (M, Msb, K;) namely, a thing; (M;) as, for instance,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA^amaAnapa A_ilaY A^holihaA","text_ar":"الاَمَانَةَ اـِلَى اهْلِهَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the thing committed to his trust and care, to its owner"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (Msb:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he delivered it, gave it up,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"surrendered it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he payed it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"discharged it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K;) namely, his debt, (S,) a bloodwit, a responsibility, and the like; (Msb in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"grm","text_ar":"غرم"},{"kind":"text","text":";) [and hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ad~aY maA","text_ar":"اَدَّى مَا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ealayohi","text_ar":"عَلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he acquitted himself of that which was incumbent on him;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"payed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"discharged, what he owed"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (T:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he performed, fulfilled,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"accomplished, it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"namely, [for instance,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlHaj~a","text_ar":"الحَجَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the pilgrimage"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; (Msb in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qDY","text_ar":"قضى"},{"kind":"text","text":";) and in like manner,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlmanaAsika","text_ar":"المَنَاسِكَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the religious rites and ceremonies of the pilgrimage"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Jel in ii. 196, and Msb ubi suprà.) It is said in the Kur [xliv. 17],"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ano A^ad~uwA A_laY~a EibaAda A@ll~`hi","text_ar":"اَنْ اَدُّوا اـلَىَّ عِبَادَ ا@للّٰهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Deliver ye to me"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the servants of God,"},{"kind":"text","text":"] the children of Israel: or, as some say, the meaning is,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ad~uwA A_ilaY~a","text_ar":"اَدُّوا اـِلَىَّ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA A^amarakumu A@ll~`hu bihi yaA EibaAdaA@ll~`hi","text_ar":"مَا اَمَرَكُمُ ا@للّٰهُ بِهِ يَا عِبَادَا@للّٰهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"perform ye to me that which God hath commanded you"},{"kind":"text","text":"to do,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"O servants of God"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: or it may mean"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"listen ye,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"give ye ear, to me;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as though the speaker said,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ad~uwA A_ilaY~a samoEakumo","text_ar":"اَدُّوا اـِلَىَّ سَمْعَكُمْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; the verb being used in this sense by the Arabs. (T.) And one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lahu","text_ar":"لَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tA^ad~ayotu","text_ar":"تاَدَّيْتُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mino Haq~ihi","text_ar":"مِنْ حَقِّهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K, TA,) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_layohi","text_ar":"اـلَيْهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in the place of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lahu","text_ar":"لَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ad~ayotuhu","text_ar":"اَدَّيْتُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (TA;) i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I payed him his due,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"right."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA.) And a man says, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA A^adoriY kayofa A^ataA^ad~aY","text_ar":"مَا اَدْرِى كَيْفَ اَتَاَدَّى","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I know not how to pay"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) One says also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^d~Y Eanohu","text_ar":"ادّى عَنْهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He payed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"made satisfaction, for him"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^d~Y","text_ar":"ادّى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eanohu AlxaraAja","text_ar":"عَنْهُ الخَرَاجَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He payed for him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in his stead, the land-tax"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (Mgh in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jzA^","text_ar":"جزا"},{"kind":"text","text":".) [Hence,] El-Akhnas says,"},{"kind":"quote","text":"faA^ad~ayotu Ean~iY maA A@sotaEartu mina AlS~ibaA\n                      \n                     \n                        wa lilomaAli EinodiYi Alyawoma raAEK wa kaAsibu"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"But I have put away from me"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what I had borrowed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"assumed, of the folishness of youth, and amorous dalliance,"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and now I am"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"there is at my abode"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a keeper and collector to the camels,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cattle,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"property."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Ham p. 346.) ―         -b2-  ["},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ad~aY A_ilY ka*aA","text_ar":"اَدَّى اـِلى كَذَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"is a phrase often used as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It brought, conducted, led,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"conduced, to such a thing"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"state;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as, for instance, crime to punishment or to ignominy.]"}],"source_refs":["T","S","K","M","Msb","TA"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}